699
01:30:40,268 --> 01:30:42,634
Arrêtez-le !

700
01:30:42,770 --> 01:30:45,830
Monsieur ! Monsieur !

701
01:30:45,973 --> 01:30:51,912
Lâchez-moi, connards !
Monsieur !

702
01:30:52,046 --> 01:30:53,809
